# Top-level safety net for the helmdesk monorepo. Per-package .gitignore files
# (helmdesk-api/, helmdesk-ui/) cover the specifics; this catches anything at the root.
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
.env
.env.local
**/.env
!**/.env.example
*.log
logs/
.DS_Store
**/dist/
coverage/

# assets/ IS committed — logo (icon.svg, icon-512.png) and preview images are deliverables.
